title: Starting out on YouTube.
body:
Just started out on youtube, and i could really use some constructive critisism/ feedback on what i need to improve on and what im doing well.
Please voice your opinion, everything helps.
Thanks
Channel - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYGFMvIKcCOYSJHN2BIKSVg

replies.body:
Because you keep posting this, I am going to say something.

Stop, please we know you want feedback but nagging us will drive us away

Just another one of those league channels starting out.
Nothing special, so I'll just same the same thing as I usually say.

Good luck, and buy a ward. You need to vision on what you're getting into.

I know perfectly well what I'm getting into.
But thanks for your opinion
